            "title": "盤中速報 - 奧多比系統(ADBE-US)大漲5.02%，報236.67美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>奧多比系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ADBE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ADBE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ADBE-US</a>)截至台北時間14日00:06股價上漲11.32美元，報236.67美元，漲幅5.02%，成交量2,498,290（股），盤中最高價236.69美元、最低價226.50美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.35%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.1%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.31%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.1%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>奧多比系統(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ADBE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ADBE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ADBE-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-7.23%</li> <li>近 1 月：-16.47%</li> <li>近 3 月：-31.22%</li> <li>近 6 月：-33.23%</li> <li>今年以來：-35.61%</li></ul></section></main>",
